{"tid":2113273,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（爆了爆了!）內地新增22宗確診病例　包括新疆16宗 (09:42)","createTime":"2020-07-18T04:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T10:52:39.000Z","uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8e33f647e4a14e2686ee0662f414c19a2094f4","tid":2113273,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"國家衛健委公布昨日（17日）內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情，新增確診病例22宗，包括6宗輸入病例（廣東3宗、山東2宗、福建1宗）及16宗本土病例（均在新疆），累計確診病例83,644宗；無新增死亡病例，維持累計4634宗。<br />\n<br />\n北京昨日無新增病例，是新發地批發市場爆發疫情以來連續第12天無新增病例。由6月11日至昨日，北京維持累計本土病例335宗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20200718/s00004/1595036170760/新冠肺炎-內地新增22宗確診病例-包括新疆16宗\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20200718%2Fs00004%2F1595036170760%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E22%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%96%B0%E7%96%8616%E5%AE%97&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=ba635d0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20200718%2Fs00004%2F1595036170760%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E22%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%96%B0%E7%96%8616%E5%AE%97&h=bcd2a23f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20200718/s00004/1595036170760/新冠肺炎-內地新增22宗確診病例-包括新疆16宗</a>"},{"pid":"22a7e316a8102a038bd2047998acf57d03aa0128","tid":2113273,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:10:23.000Z","msg":"今次到新疆大爆發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889caa8e4e0d1fd49addde6ac8a8f0792e725e06","tid":2113273,"uid":9328,"like":0,"